subject: United States Reconciliation
body:
United States Reconciliation Committee
1114 6th Ave #17thW.
R. Grace Building, New York,
NY 10110, USA
Attn: Sir/ Madam..
Do you know that by now you should have concluded everything
concerning your transaction and receive your long overdue payment. I
will give you every detail the reasons and why all the efforts you

still keep watching you as you waste more of your time and money. For

without my concept because the foundation of that transaction was

NO body else can assist you conclude that transaction without my
involvement so STOP wasting your time because they can NOT help you

Yours in Service
Mr. Anthony Brooks

subject: Re:   United States Reconciliation
body:
Hello Mr. Anthony Brooks,

Thank you for reaching out and sharing this information with me. I must admit, I'm a bit confused about the details of what you're referring to. Could you please elaborate more on the matter? What is it that should have been concluded by now? 

I'm also curious about your role in all of this. How are you involved and why is your consent necessary for the conclusion of this matter?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
James
